@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jubvnu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.sin(wp.cos(v1 + 0.46)) * (wp.sin(v1 + 0.62) * v0))
    v1 = (tmp / v1)
    v1 = (wp.sin(tmp) - (wp.exp(v1 + 0.48) * wp.sin(v2 + 0.26)))
    tmp = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.47)) + wp.abs(0.80))
    v1 = ((tmp + (v0 + 0.32 / v2 + 0.75)) / wp.exp(v1))
    v1 = (wp.sin(v1) / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.86) * (tmp + 0.15 / v0 + 0.43)))
    data[tid] = v0
